m\": 1805, \"to\": 1815}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1835}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked if it would have been better to pull out beforehand, Carini said: \\\"I am not one that gives in easily.\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1965, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1917, \"end\": 1923, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9982273739152554, \"rank\": 0.001775773867933482, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No, even if they had said that we would not fight, I would never have accepted it.\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 2048, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have a warrior's mentality.\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2078, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a warrior's mentality\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2077}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time I did not manage.\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2106, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt too much pain on my nose.\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2139, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"too much pain\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2127}, {\"ngram\": \"my nose\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2138}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I said enough.\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2154, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not a defeat for me - for me if you go in the ring you have already won, regardless of everything else.\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2265, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a defeat\", \"from\": 2166, \"to\": 2174}, {\"ngram\": \"the ring\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2212}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not here to judge.\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2289, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not up to me to say if it's fair or not fair.\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2340,